## agGridBalhamFontFace variable

The AG Balham font face used on ag-theme-balham/ag-theme-balham-dark Grid Pro themes.

**Signature:**

```typescript
agGridBalhamFontFace = "\n  @font-face {\n    font-family: \"agGridBalham\";\n    src: url(data:font/woff2;charset=utf-8;base64,);\n    font-weight: normal;\n    font-style: normal;\n  }\n"
```
